{"id": "rios012", "name": "Audio_Yazawa_496_12_25", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "It's so late... Rin, you really don't need me to stay?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Yeah... I'm fine.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Okay. Try to get some rest. I'll come check on you tomorrow.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Dad... Mom... <i>*sob*...*sob*</i>...</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "Door Knock"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Katsuya? Did you forget something?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Rin... it's me.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n<font size=\"1.6\">Unit-Unit 10?</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I'm sorry, running here all of a sudden... I just wanted to tell you. My service position has been reset to the architecture team. Starting tomorrow, I won't be able to take care of the plants... and I won't be able to see you again.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I know Mr. Katsuya won't forgive me, so I waited until he left to talk to you... You... are you willing to open the door?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... I... Um... Perhaps you aren't able to trust me anymore, but please listen to me, just a bit... Please.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "What happened at the institute, that was my fault... I couldn't rescue Mr. Yazawa and others in time...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "But... ! I didn't do it!\nBefore, a strange Architect came to talk with me... He was basically like me, an Architect with his own consciousness... No...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "That Architect said that I'm not completely awakened. That I'm still under the control of my protocol. All I needed to do was work a little harder and I could cast it off. But I was too scared, so I didn't do anything. I acted like I didn't know anything...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I don't know if it was them who did it... but... I definitely felt like it was them who did that to the institute. I tricked myself into thinking something like this would never happen... If I had only warned everybody ahead of time, perhaps nobody would be dead. Your parents, the people in the institute, they'd all still be alive.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Mr. Katsuya was right, I killed them...\nI'm... so sorry.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Slumps Over"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...Dad, Mom...</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin? Are you there?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... <i>*sob*... *sob*</i>...</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Rin, once we talked about how our voices sound alike... Do you remember?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "That may just be a coincidence... But after knowing you, I've been so happy every day. Not like before, when I was scared of humans. Gradually, I began to like them... I can't help but think, that this coincidence might mean something...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "As an Architect, I always thought that I'd be like this forever. But since we have similar voices, maybe, just maybe... I can be like you, and live a normal life...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I really hope there's no barrier between us... Whether or not Architects have their own consciousness, I hope that one day we can live together in peace... Stupid, right? Hoping for something that'll never happen, then destroying it with my own hands... What am I, anyway...?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...Unit 10...</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Haha, Architects... I don't even have the ability to produce tears... I'm obviously upset, but I can't cry...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...<i>*sob*</i>...</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "Notification"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "It's a command for my new work... I must go.\nRin, I just want to let you know, whatever happens... As long as I can hear my own voice, I won't forget you. That's all I can be sure of.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Thank you, Rin. Thanks for everything you did for me.\n... Good-bye...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... It's already... day?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\nThis calendula... Did Unit 10 bring this...?\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "Slumps Over"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">What on earth...should I do...?</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "もうこんな時間だ……\n凛、本当にそばにいなくていいのか？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うん……大丈夫。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……わかった。\n眠れるようなら、ちゃんと寝るんだ。\nまた明日、会いに来る。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">お父さん……お母さん……\n……ひっく……ぅぅ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "ノック"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……克也？忘れ物？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……凛……私……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n<font size=\"1.6\">じゅっ……10号機？</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "突然、ごめんなさい……\nこれだけ、伝えたくて……\n私、明日から建築チームに移動することになったの。\nだから、植物の面倒を見れなくなる……あなたにも、会えなくなる。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "克也さんが私を許してくれないことはわかってる。\nだから、克也さんが帰るのを待って会いに来たの……\nドアを……開けてくれる……？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……そ、っか……\nうん……もう、私のことを信じられないとしても、これだけ聞いて……すぐに終わるから……おねがい……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "研究所のことは私が悪いの……私、矢澤博士やみんなを助けられなかった……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "でも……！あの火を付けたのは私じゃない！\n前ね、変なアーキテクトが会いに来たの……\n私と同じ……自我を持つアーキテクト……ううん……同じじゃ、ない……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "そのアーキテクトは、私はまだ完全に覚醒してないって……まだプロトコルに支配されてるって言ってた。\n頑張ればその支配から逃れられるって……\nでも、私、怖くって……何もしなかった……何も知らないふりしてた……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "今回の火事を起こしたのが彼らなのかどうかはわからない……\nでも、彼らが研究所に手を出すかもしれないことは、よく考えればわかったのに……\n信じたくなくて……「そんなこと起こるわけない」って思いこもうとしてた……\nもし、もし私がみんなに警告していれば、誰も死ななかったかもしれない。\n凛のお父さんとお母さんも……研究所の人も……まだ生きてたかもしれないのに。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "克也さんの言うとおりだよ。\n私が、みんなを殺したの……\n本当に……ごめんなさい……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "崩れ落ちる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……お父さん、お母さん……</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凛？そこに、いる？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……っ……うう……</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……凛、私たちの声が似てるって話をしたこと……覚えてる？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "それはただの偶然かもしれないけど……でも、あなたに出会ってから毎日とっても楽しかった。\n前みたいに人類が怖くなくなった。\nううん、それどころか少しずつ好きになることができたの……\nだからね、こう思わずにはいられないんだ。\nこれは必然だったんじゃないかって……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "アーキテクトである私は、永遠にこのままなんだろうって思ってた。\nでも、もしかしたら……もしかしたら、同じ声を持つあなたと普通の人として過ごせるかもしれない……なんて……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私たちの間にある隔たりなんてなくなればいい……\nアーキテクトに自我があってもなくても、いつか……ともに平和に暮らせる日が来ればいいのに……なんて……バカみたいでしょ？\nこんな現実的じゃない夢を抱きながら、私は自分でそれを壊したの……私って、なんなんだろうね……？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……10号機……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "はは……今も……\nアーキテクトには涙を作る機能なんてないから……悲しいのに……すごくすごく悲しいのに……私は泣けない……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……うう……っ……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "新しい仕事の通知だ……行かないと。\n凛、これからどうなってしまっても、私は私の声を聞くたびにあなたを思い出すよ。\nそれだけ……あなたに伝えたかった……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "ありがとう、凛。\n……さようなら……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……もう、朝？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………！\nキンセンカ……10号機が……？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "崩れ落ちる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">私……どうしたらいいの……</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "好晚了……凜，真的不需要我留下來嗎？\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗯……我沒問題的。\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……好。試著睡一下吧，我明天再來看妳。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">爸爸……媽媽……嗚嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "敲門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……克也？忘了拿東西嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……凜……是我。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n<font size=\"1.6\">十、十號機？</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "對不起，突然跑來……只是想告訴妳，我的服務單位被重設到建築組。從明天開始，我沒辦法再照料植物……也不能再見到妳了。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我知道克也先生不會原諒我，所以等他走了我才來找妳……妳……願意開門嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……這樣啊……那……也許妳不願意再相信我，但請聽我說說話，一下就好……拜託。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "研究所的事，是我的錯……我來不及救矢澤博士他們……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "但是……！真的不是我做的！\n之前，有一個奇怪的建造者跑來找我搭話……他大概和我一樣，都是擁有自我意識的建造者……不對……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "那個建造者說，我並沒有完全覺醒，還是受到協定的控制。只要我努力一點，應該能夠掙脫它……但我實在太過害怕，所以什麼都不做，對你們也假裝什麼都不知道……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我不知道是不是他們做的……但……明明察覺到他們可能對研究所下手，我還是欺騙自己「這種事不會發生」……如果我先警告大家，也許就沒有人會死。凜的父母、研究所的人們，現在都還能活著。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "克也先生說的對，是我殺了他們……\n真的……很對不起。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "坐倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……爸爸、媽媽……</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "凜？妳在那裡嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……凜，我們聊過彼此聲音相像的事……妳還記得吧？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "雖然只是巧合……但認識妳之後，我每天都好快樂，不再像以前那樣害怕人類，甚至慢慢開始喜歡上他們……我忍不住在想，這個巧合是不是代表了什麼意義……\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "身為建造者，我曾以為自己會永遠保持這樣。但既然我們有相同的聲音，也許，只是也許……我能和妳一樣，過著普通人的生活……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "好希望我們之間沒有那麼多隔閡……無論建造者有沒有自己的意識，我都希望有一天我們能和平共處……很傻對吧？擅自懷抱著不切實際的願望，又親手毀掉了它……這樣的我，又算什麼呢……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……十號機……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "哈哈，現在也是……建造者並沒有流淚的功能……明明很難過，但就是哭不出來……\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……嗚……</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "通知"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "是新的工作指令……我得走了。\n凜，我只想說，不管以後會怎麼樣……只要聽見自己的聲音，我就不會忘記妳。這是我唯一確定的事。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "謝謝妳，凜，謝謝妳對我做的一切。\n……再見……\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……已經……白天了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n這盆金盞花……是十號機拿來的……？\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "坐倒"], "content": ""}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">我到底……該怎麼辦才好……</font>\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "이렇게 늦었는데... Rin, 정말 내가 곁에 안 남아줘도 괜찮겠어?\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응... 괜찮아.\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......알았어. 우선 자도록 해. 내일 다시 보러올 테니까.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "문이 닫힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">아빠..... 엄마... 흐흑...</font>\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Knock_Door", "노크"], "content": ""}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......Katsuya? 뭐 두고 갔어?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......Rin... 나야.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n <font size=\"1.6\">10... 10호기?</font>\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "미안해... 갑자기 달아나버려서... 내 본래 업무가 건축 쪽으로 변경 됐어...그냥 네게 말해주고 싶어서.\n 내일부터는 그쪽에서 일하게 될 거야. 그래서 이제는 식물들을 돌봐주는 것도... 널 다시 만나는 것도 힘들 것 같아.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Katsuya 씨가 날 용서하지 못 할 거란 것도 알고 있어. 그래서 Katsuya 씨가 없는 시간에 이렇게 널 찾아온 거야... 괜찮다면... 문 좀 열어줄 수 있어?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...그렇구나... 저기... 네가 나를 믿지 못 할 수도 있지만, 그래도 내가 하는 말을 들어줬으면 좋겠어... 잠깐이라도... 부탁이야.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "연구소의 일은... 내 잘못이야... 박사님들을 제시간에 구해내질 못했어...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하지만...! 정말 내가 저지른 짓이 아니야!\n그전에, 어떤 이상한 아키텍트가 나를 찾아왔고 어떤 얘기를 해줬는데... 그 아키텍트도 나랑 비슷하게 자신만의 사고와 의지를 가지고 있었어... 아니지...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그 아키텍트는 내가 완전히 각성하지 못했다면서... 그리고 아직도 협정 프로토콜의 통제를 받고 있다고 말했어. 내가 조금만 노력하면, 나도 그 통제에서 벗어날 수 있다면서... 하지만... 난 너무 무서웠어. 그래서 아무 짓도 하지 않았고... 너희들에게도 아무것도 알지 못하는 척했던 거야...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "그 아키텍트들이 저지른 짓인지 아닌지는 모르겠지만... 그래도 그 자들이 언젠가는 연구소에 손을 댈 수 있을 거라는 걸 알고 있으면서도... \"그런 일은 일어나지 않을 거야\" 라고 내 스스로를 속였어....만약 내가 모두에게 미리 알려줬다면, 아마 아무도 죽지 않았을 거야...\nRin의 부모님도... 연구소의 사람들도... 지금 모두 살아있었을 거야.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Katsuya 씨가 한 말이 맞아. 결국 내가 그 분들을 죽인 거야...\n정말... 정말 미안해.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Impact", "주저 앉는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...아빠... 엄마...</font>\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Rin? 거기에 있는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......흐흑........</font>\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......Rin, 우리 둘의 목소리... 닮은 적이 있다고 그런 얘길 했었지...? 아직 기억 나?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "우연일지라도... 널 만나고 나서부터 나는 매일 즐거운 나날을 보낼 수 있었어. 예전처럼 인간들을 무서워하지 않으면서 말이야. 심지어... 조금씩 인간들을 좋아하게 됐으니까... 나는 우리 목소리가 닮았다는 우연이 아니라 뭔가 의미가 있는 것은 아닐까 끊임없이 생각했었어...\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아키텍트로서도 영원히 그렇게 살아갈 수 있을 줄 알았는데... 하지만 너와 닮은 목소리를 가지게 된 것만으로도... 아마... 너처럼 보통 인간의 삶을 지낼 수 있었는지도 몰라...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "우리들 사이에 수많은 벽들이 없어지고... 아키텍트가 자아를 가지고 있든 없든... 우리가 함께 평화롭게 공존할 수 있는 그런 날이 꼭 왔으면 좋겠어... 엄청 바보 같지? 내 멋대로 현실에 맞지 않는 꿈을 가졌으면서 또 멋대로 그 꿈을 접는다니... 이런 나는... 대체 뭘까...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......10호기......</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "하하... 지금도 마찬가지네... 아키텍트에게 눈물을 흘리는 기능 따윈 없어... 분명 이렇게나 슬픈데... 울지도 못해...\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">......흑......</font>\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["sound_imnotification", "통지"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "새로운 업무 지령이 내려졌어... 난 이제 가봐야만 해.\nRin, 난 그저... 나중에 어떻게 되든.... 스스로 내 목소리를 듣기만 한다면 너를 잊지 않고 살아갈 수 있다고 말해주고 싶었어. 이 사실만큼은 확실하게 말해줄 수 있으니까...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "네가 내게 해주었던 모든 일들... 전부 고마워, Rin... \n...그럼 안녕...\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...벌써... 낮인가?\n"},